devdoc.author: Polkadot Builders
devdoc.details: This contract allows for the creation and execution of auctions for Polkadot Builder Crests NFTs.

params.tokenId: The ID of the token to burn.

constructor.details: Constructor function that sets the initial values for the Polkadot Builder Crest contract.

params._auctionHouse: The address of the auction house contract.
params._founders: The address of the founders who will receive tokens.
params._store: The address of the store contract.

delegate(address).details: Delegates votes from the sender to `delegatee`.

delegates(address).details: Returns the delegate that `account` has chosen.

getPastTotalSupply(uint256).details: Returns the total supply of votes available at the end of a past block (`blockNumber`). NOTE: This value is the sum of all available votes, which is not necessarily the sum of all delegated votes. Votes that have not been delegated are still part of total supply, even though they would not participate in a vote. Requirements: - `blockNumber` must have been already mined

getPastVotes(address,uint256).details: Returns the amount of votes that `account` had at the end of a past block (`blockNumber`). Requirements: - `blockNumber` must have been already mined

getVotes(address).details: Returns the current amount of votes that `account` has.

mint().details: Only the auction house contract can call this function.

mintSpecific(address,uint96).details: Only the contract owner can call this function.

params.dna: The DNA value for the token.
params.to: The address to receive the token.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

setAuctionHouse(address).details: Only the contract owner can call this function.

params._auctionHouse: The address of the auction house contract.

setContractURI(string).details: Only the contract owner can call this function.

setFounders(address).details: Only the contract owner can call this function.

params._founders: The address of the founders account.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

devdoc.title: Polkadot Builder Crest NFT

burn(uint256).notice: Burns a token with the specified ID.

contractURI().notice: Returns the URI of the contract metadata.

mint().notice: Mints a new token for the auction house.

mintSpecific(address,uint96).notice: Mints a new token to a specific address with a given DNA.

setAuctionHouse(address).notice: Sets the address of the auction house contract.

setContractURI(string).notice: Sets the URI of the contract metadata.

setFounders(address).notice: Sets the address of the founders account.

tokenURI(uint256).notice: Returns the URI of the token metadata.
